<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٧٩ ... سُورَةُ النَّازِعَاتِ ... آياتها ٤٦ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالنَّازِعَاتِ}</span> ... قَسَمٌ بِالمَلَائِكَةِ تَنْزِعُ أَرْوَاحَ الكُفَّارِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{غَرْقًا}</span> ... نَزْعًا شَدِيدًا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالنَّاشِطَاتِ}</span> ... قَسَمٌ بِالمَلَائِكَةِ تَسُلُّ أَرْوَاحَ المُؤْمِنِينَ بِرِفْقٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالسَّابِحَاتِ}</span> ... قَسَمٌ بِالمَلَائِكَةِ الَّتِي تَسْبَحُ فِي نُزُولِهَا مِنَ السَّمَاءِ، وَصُعُودِها إِلَيْهَا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَالسَّابِقَاتِ}</span> ... قَسَمٌ بِالمَلَائِكَةِ الَّتِي تَسْبِقُ الشَّيَاطِينَ بِالوَحْيِ إِلَى الأَنْبِيَاء؛ لِئَلَّا تَسْتَرِقَهُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَالْمُدَبِّرَاتِ أَمْرًا}</span> ... قَسَمٌ بِالمَلَائِكَةِ المُنَفِّذَاتِ أَمْرَ اللهِ، وَجَوابُ القَسَمِ مَحْذُوفٌ،<span class="c5"> وَتَقْدِيرُهُ:</span> لَتُبْعَثُنَّ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَرْجُفُ الرَّاجِفَةُ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> تَضْطَرِبُ الأَرْضُ بِالنَّفْخَةِ الأُولَى:</span> نَفْخَةِ الصَّعْقِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَتْبَعُهَا الرَّادِفَةُ}</span> ... تَلِيهَا نَفْخَةٌ أُخْرَى لِلْبَعْثِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَاجِفَةٌ}</span> ... خَائِفَةٌ، مُضْطَرِبَةٌ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَاشِعَةٌ}</span> ... ذَلِيلَةٌ مِنْ هَوْلِ مَا تُشَاهِدُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْحَافِرَةِ}</span> ... الحَالَةِ الَّتِي كُنَّا عَلَيْهَا فَي الأَرْضِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَّخِرَةً}</span> ... بَالِيَةً.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَرَّةٌ خَاسِرَةٌ}</span> ... رَجْعَةٌ خَائِبَةٌ ذَاتُ خُسْرَانٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{زَجْرَةٌ}</span> ... نَفْخَةٌ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>